  "text": "```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Night Theme Landing Page</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body class=\"bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 min-h-screen flex flex-col\">\n    <header class=\"bg-black bg-opacity-50 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-gray-800 sticky top-0 z-50\">\n        <nav class=\"container mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex justify-between items-center\">\n            <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4\">\n                <div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold\">NL</div>\n                <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold\">Night Landing</h1>\n            </div>\n            <ul class=\"flex space-x-6\">\n                <li><a href=\"#home\" class=\"hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors\">Home</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#features\" class=\"hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors\">Features</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\" class=\"hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors\">About</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"flex-1 container mx-auto px-4 py-8\">\n        <section id=\"home\" class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-5xl font-black mb-4 text-gradient from-purple-400 to-blue-500 bg-clip-text\">\n                Welcome to the Night\n            </h2>\n            <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">\n                Experience the elegance of darkness with subtle glows and refined design.\n            </p>\n            <button class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-lg shadow-xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-all\">\n                Get Started\n            </button>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"features\" class=\"mb-16\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-3xl font-black mb-8 text-center text-gradient from-green-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text\">\n                Features\n            </h3>\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n                <div class=\"bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all\">\n                    <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-3xl text-white\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-moon\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\">Dark Elegance</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">\n                        Refined dark backgrounds with subtle glow accents create a\n                        sophisticated atmosphere that's easy on the eyes.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all\">\n                    <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-3xl text-white\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-star\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\">Subtle Glows</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">\n                        Carefully crafted glow effects highlight important elements\n                        without overwhelming the elegant dark theme.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all\">\n                    <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-3xl text-white\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-eye\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\">Eye Comfort</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">\n                        Muted colors and proper contrast ratios ensure comfortable\n                        viewing during extended periods in low-light environments.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"mb-16\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-3xl font-black mb-8 text-center text-gradient from-purple-400 to-blue-500 bg-clip-text\">\n                About Night Theme\n            </h3>\n            <div class=\" bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 shadow-lg\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4\">\n                    The <span class=\"font-semibold text-gradient from-blue-500 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text\">Night Theme</span> was designed with\n                    sophistication and comfort in mind. Every element is carefully\n                    crafted to create an immersive experience that balances beauty with\n                    functionality.\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-gray-700 p-6 rounded-lg\">\n                        <h4 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gradient from-purple-400 to-blue-500 bg-clip-text\">\n                            Mood Lighting\n                        </h4>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">\n                            Soft ambient colors create the perfect mood for night-time\n                            browsing.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bg-gray-700 p-6 rounded-lg\">\n                        <h4 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gradient from-blue-400 to-green-500 bg-clip-text\">\n                            Responsive Design\n                        </h4>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">\n                            Beautiful experience across all devices, from phones to large\n                            desktop displays.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer class=\"bg-gray-900 border-t border-gray-800\">\n        <div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 py-6 flex justify-between items-center\">\n            <p class=\"text-gray-400\">&copy; 2024 Night Landing. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <div class=\"flex space-x-4\">\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors\">\n                    <i class=\"fab fa-twitter\"></i>\n                </a>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors\">\n                    <i class=\"fab fa-github\"></i>\n                </a>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors\">\n                    <i class=\"fab fa-discord\"></i>\n                </a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"
